metadata.name: Souvenirs d' Antan...SanctusDei
metadata.description: Souvenirs d' Antan is in fact a physical work on a wooden panel, with an audioBox in the center, as it is in fact a part of an Interior Design Appartment. Commanded by Darko Stojan, my partner, it is in fact combination of our memories from divers occasions / Opera Ljubljana, Ljubljana Castle...Combination of photos continues by insertion of photos in Tokio by well known photographer. A central female figure is drawn by Indian Ink, colors, collages, imitation of gold mixed by another souvenir , an glass perfume bottle...
